01:23:31,480 --> 01:23:34,350
今天，Stevens先生,
Today... Mr. Stevens,

1229
01:23:34,441 --> 01:23:36,003
我很惊喜
I was surprised.

1230
01:23:36,168 --> 01:23:39,285
你已经领导了民族平等的运动30年了
You’ve led the battle for
race equality for thirty years!

1231
01:23:44,933 --> 01:23:48,316
对国家的未来来说，这是每个希望的基础
The basis of... of every hope
for this country’s future life,

1232
01:23:48,410 --> 01:23:51,413
你否认黑人平等
you denied Negro equality!
