早上好，Jim
LINCOLN: Morning, Jim.

1254
01:25:37,437 --> 01:25:38,924
您好，总统先生
ARMY SURGEON: Hello, Mr. President.

1255
01:25:38,975 --> 01:25:40,594
很高兴又看到你了
LINCOLN: Good to see you again.

